# .trivyignore — CVE deferral list for AgentOS
#
# Format: one CVE ID per line. Always include a comment with:
#   - Why this is being ignored
#   - The reviewer (initials)
#   - An expiry date (after which the entry should be re-reviewed)
#
# Empty lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored by Trivy.
#
# DO NOT add entries here without a justification. A 6-month-old `# false
# positive` with no name and no date is functionally the same as broken
# security.

# (No active deferrals. Add CVEs below this line when needed.)
